{"tid":1557464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"竟敢性侵女生！黑幫動犬刑 咬爛他下體","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:59:31.000Z","uid":292267,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7508328f602d23b8016845427876de7a33f0128","tid":1557464,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/177575?from=webpush\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2FArticle%2F177575%3Ffrom%3Dwebpush&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=edcf70a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/177575?from=webpush</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/09/10/1568121301_44346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F09%2F10%2F1568121301_44346.jpg&h=49b186ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，事發於今（2019）年8月，墨西哥首都墨西哥市，一名30歲左右的男子，被指控性侵一名女子，因此被黑幫分子盯上，約5名黑幫分子將男子上銬，接著壓制在地，接著黑幫分子放出2隻比特犬，一隻白色的比特犬接近男子的下體，最終狠狠撕咬男子下半身，當場血肉模糊，男子更是痛到尖叫。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Metro》報導，近日墨西哥動用私刑的殘忍程度逐步上升，且這種情形越來越頻繁，光是今年上半年，就有超過1萬7000人遭黑幫分子殺害，其中還不包含槍擊、綁架、人口偷渡等犯罪。而墨西哥每天都會有數十名婦女遭到性侵，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甚至有未成年女孩遭到警察性侵</strong></span>，根據聯合國統計指出，墨西哥每天平均會有9名女性被殺害，不過官方的性侵案數據卻遠遠低於其他國家，因為墨西哥普遍不信任警方，因此報案民眾並不多。"},{"pid":"962428f2e4ae01d6a2dac4f6b5e95c7c7ef457b5","tid":1557464,"uid":26773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"慘過死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人有佢地一半咁勇既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9fbecccb837ae1b446bbc16f6573460442e5a4","tid":1557464,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"人地既老黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore